#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:21.1"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, aggivessana, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:21.2"
msgid ""
"yo nu kho dukkhaṃ allīno dukkhaṃ upagato dukkhaṃ ajjhosito, dukkhaṃ ‘etaṃ "
"mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ti samanupassati, api nu kho so sāmaṃ vā "
"dukkhaṃ parijāneyya, dukkhaṃ vā parikkhepetvā vihareyyā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:21.3"
msgid "“Kiñhi siyā, bho gotama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:21.4"
msgid "No hidaṃ, bho gotamā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:21.5"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññasi, aggivessana, "
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:21.6"
msgid ""
"nanu tvaṃ evaṃ sante dukkhaṃ allīno dukkhaṃ upagato dukkhaṃ ajjhosito, "
"dukkhaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:21.7"
msgid "‘etaṃ mama, esohamasmi, eso me attā’ti samanupassasī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:21.8"
msgid "“Kiñhi no siyā, bho gotama?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:21.9"
msgid "Evametaṃ, bho gotamā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya22"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.234"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
#. VAR: kuṭhāriṃ → kudhāriṃ (s1-3, km, mr)
msgctxt "mn35:22.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, aggivessana, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ "
"caramāno tiṇhaṃ kuṭhāriṃ ādāya vanaṃ paviseyya."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: akukkukajātaṃ → akukkuṭajātaṃ (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn35:22.2"
msgid "So tattha passeyya mahantaṃ kadalikkhandhaṃ ujuṃ navaṃ akukkukajātaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: vinibbhujeyya → vinibbhujjeyya (mr)
msgctxt "mn35:22.3"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ mūle chindeyya, mūle chetvā agge chindeyya, agge chetvā pattavaṭṭiṃ "
"vinibbhujeyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.4"
msgid ""
"So tattha pattavaṭṭiṃ vinibbhujanto pheggumpi nādhigaccheyya, kuto sāraṃ?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.5"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho tvaṃ, aggivessana, mayā sakasmiṃ vāde samanuyuñjiyamāno "
"samanugāhiyamāno samanubhāsiyamāno ritto tuccho aparaddho."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.6"
msgid "Bhāsitā kho pana te esā, aggivessana, vesāliyaṃ parisati vācā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.7"
msgid ""
"‘nāhaṃ taṃ passāmi samaṇaṃ vā brāhmaṇaṃ vā, saṃghiṃ gaṇiṃ gaṇācariyaṃ, api "
"arahantaṃ sammāsambuddhaṃ paṭijānamānaṃ, yo mayā vādena vādaṃ samāraddho na "
"saṅkampeyya na sampakampeyya na sampavedheyya, yassa na kacchehi sedā "
"mucceyyuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.8"
msgid ""
"Thūṇaṃ cepāhaṃ acetanaṃ vādena vādaṃ samārabheyyaṃ sāpi mayā vādena vādaṃ "
"samāraddhā saṅkampeyya sampakampeyya sampavedheyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.9"
msgid "Ko pana vādo manussabhūtassā’ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.10"
msgid ""
"Tuyhaṃ kho pana, aggivessana, appekaccāni sedaphusitāni nalāṭā muttāni, "
"uttarāsaṅgaṃ vinibhinditvā bhūmiyaṃ patiṭṭhitāni."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.11"
msgid "Mayhaṃ kho pana, aggivessana, natthi etarahi kāyasmiṃ sedo”ti."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: tasmiṃ → tassaṃ (?)
msgctxt "mn35:22.12"
msgid "Iti bhagavā tasmiṃ parisati suvaṇṇavaṇṇaṃ kāyaṃ vivari."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:22.13"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vutte, saccako nigaṇṭhaputto tuṇhībhūto maṅkubhūto pattakkhandho "
"adhomukho pajjhāyanto appaṭibhāno nisīdi."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya23"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:23.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho dummukho licchaviputto saccakaṃ nigaṇṭhaputtaṃ tuṇhībhūtaṃ "
"maṅkubhūtaṃ pattakkhandhaṃ adhomukhaṃ pajjhāyantaṃ appaṭibhānaṃ viditvā "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.2"
msgid "“upamā maṃ, bhagavā, paṭibhātī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.3"
msgid "“Paṭibhātu taṃ, dummukhā”ti bhagavā avoca."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.4"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhante, gāmassa vā nigamassa vā avidūre pokkharaṇī."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.5"
msgid "Tatrāssa kakkaṭako."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.6"
msgid ""
"Atha kho, bhante, sambahulā kumārakā vā kumārikā vā tamhā gāmā vā nigamā vā "
"nikkhamitvā yena sā pokkharaṇī tenupasaṅkameyyuṃ; upasaṅkamitvā taṃ "
"pokkharaṇiṃ ogāhetvā taṃ kakkaṭakaṃ udakā uddharitvā thale patiṭṭhāpeyyuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.7"
msgid ""
"Yaññadeva hi so, bhante, kakkaṭako aḷaṃ abhininnāmeyya taṃ tadeva te "
"kumārakā vā kumārikā vā kaṭṭhena vā kathalena vā sañchindeyyuṃ sambhañjeyyuṃ "
"sampalibhañjeyyuṃ."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.8"
msgid ""
"Evañhi so, bhante, kakkaṭako sabbehi aḷehi sañchinnehi sambhaggehi "
"sampalibhaggehi abhabbo taṃ pokkharaṇiṃ puna otarituṃ, seyyathāpi pubbe."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: vipphanditāni tānipi sabbāni → vipphanditāni kānici kānici tāni (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "mn35:23.9"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, bhante, yāni saccakassa nigaṇṭhaputtassa visūkāyitāni "
"visevitāni vipphanditāni tānipi sabbāni bhagavatā sañchinnāni sambhaggāni "
"sampalibhaggāni;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:23.10"
msgid ""
"abhabbo ca dāni, bhante, saccako nigaṇṭhaputto puna bhagavantaṃ "
"upasaṅkamituṃ yadidaṃ vādādhippāyo”ti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya24"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:24.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, saccako nigaṇṭhaputto dummukhaṃ licchaviputtaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

#. VAR: () → (mukharosi tvaṃ dummukha) (bj, s1-3, km)
#. VAR: āgamehi tvaṃ, dummukha → etthantare pāṭho sī potthake
msgctxt "mn35:24.2"
msgid ""
"“āgamehi tvaṃ, dummukha,āgamehi tvaṃ, dummukha, () na mayaṃ tayā saddhiṃ "
"mantema, idha mayaṃ bhotā gotamena saddhiṃ mantema."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.235"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:24.3"
msgid ""
"Tiṭṭhatesā, bho gotama, amhākañceva aññesañca puthusamaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ vācā."
msgstr ""

# The point of this passage is for Saccaka to, semi-sincerely, wriggle out of his initial statement. Translating the person as plural is misleading, as it can easily be read as referring to “our” (the Buddha and Saccaka’s), whereas it really refers to Saccaka’s initial claim; Saccaka has been using plural for himself. Next, consider this phrase. Vilapa is used in the suttas not quite in the sense of “prattle”, which is a babble or torrent of meaningless speech, but rather simply an empty or hollow claim. What he’s doing here is the same as modern trolls who claim their idea are meant “ironically”.
msgctxt "mn35:24.4"
msgid "Vilāpaṃ vilapitaṃ maññe."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:24.5"
msgid ""
"Kittāvatā ca nu kho bhoto gotamassa sāvako sāsanakaro hoti ovādapatikaro "
"tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṅkatho vesārajjappatto aparappaccayo satthusāsane "
"viharatī”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:24.6"
msgid ""
"“Idha, aggivessana, mama sāvako yaṃ kiñci rūpaṃ atītānāgatapaccuppannaṃ "
"ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā oḷārikaṃ vā sukhumaṃ vā hīnaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā yaṃ "
"dūre santike vā, sabbaṃ rūpaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti "
"evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya passati;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:24.7"
msgid "yā kāci vedanā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:24.8"
msgid "yā kāci saññā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:24.9"
msgid "ye keci saṅkhārā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:24.10"
msgid ""
"yaṃ kiñci viññāṇaṃ atītānāgatapaccuppannaṃ ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā oḷārikaṃ "
"vā sukhumaṃ vā hīnaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā, yaṃ dūre santike vā, sabbaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘"
"netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"passati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:24.11"
msgid ""
"Ettāvatā kho, aggivessana, mama sāvako sāsanakaro hoti ovādapatikaro "
"tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṅkatho vesārajjappatto aparappaccayo satthusāsane "
"viharatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya25"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:25.1"
msgid ""
"“Kittāvatā pana, bho gotama, bhikkhu arahaṃ hoti khīṇāsavo vusitavā "
"katakaraṇīyo ohitabhāro anuppattasadattho parikkhīṇabhavasaṃyojano "
"sammadaññāvimutto”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:25.2"
msgid ""
"“Idha, aggivessana, bhikkhu yaṃ kiñci rūpaṃ atītānāgatapaccuppannaṃ "
"ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā oḷārikaṃ vā sukhumaṃ vā hīnaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā yaṃ "
"dūre santike vā sabbaṃ rūpaṃ ‘netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti "
"evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya disvā anupādā vimutto hoti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:25.3"
msgid "yā kāci vedanā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:25.4"
msgid "yā kāci saññā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:25.5"
msgid "ye keci saṅkhārā … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:25.6"
msgid ""
"yaṃ kiñci viññāṇaṃ atītānāgatapaccuppannaṃ ajjhattaṃ vā bahiddhā vā oḷārikaṃ "
"vā sukhumaṃ vā hīnaṃ vā paṇītaṃ vā yaṃ dūre santike vā sabbaṃ viññāṇaṃ ‘"
"netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ti evametaṃ yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"disvā anupādā vimutto hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:25.7"
msgid ""
"Ettāvatā kho, aggivessana, bhikkhu arahaṃ hoti khīṇāsavo vusitavā "
"katakaraṇīyo ohitabhāro anuppattasadattho parikkhīṇabhavasaṃyojano "
"sammadaññāvimutto."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya26"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:26.1"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vimuttacitto kho, aggivessana, bhikkhu tīhi anuttariyehi samannāgato "
"hoti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:26.2"
msgid "dassanānuttariyena, paṭipadānuttariyena, vimuttānuttariyena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:26.3"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vimuttacitto kho, aggivessana, bhikkhu tathāgataññeva sakkaroti garuṃ "
"karoti māneti pūjeti—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:26.4"
msgid ""
"buddho so bhagavā bodhāya dhammaṃ deseti, danto so bhagavā damathāya dhammaṃ "
"deseti, santo so bhagavā samathāya dhammaṃ deseti, tiṇṇo so bhagavā taraṇāya "
"dhammaṃ deseti, parinibbuto so bhagavā parinibbānāya dhammaṃ desetī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya27"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.236"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:27.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:27.2"
msgid ""
"“mayameva, bho gotama, dhaṃsī, mayaṃ pagabbā, ye mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ "
"vādena vādaṃ āsādetabbaṃ amaññimha."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:27.3"
msgid ""
"Siyā hi, bho gotama, hatthiṃ pabhinnaṃ āsajja purisassa sotthibhāvo, na "
"tveva bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ āsajja siyā purisassa sotthibhāvo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:27.4"
msgid ""
"Siyā hi, bho gotama, pajjalitaṃ aggikkhandhaṃ āsajja purisassa sotthibhāvo, "
"na tveva bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ āsajja siyā purisassa sotthibhāvo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:27.5"
msgid ""
"Siyā hi, bho gotama, āsīvisaṃ ghoravisaṃ āsajja purisassa sotthibhāvo, na "
"tveva bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ āsajja siyā purisassa sotthibhāvo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:27.6"
msgid ""
"Mayameva, bho gotama, dhaṃsī, mayaṃ pagabbā, ye mayaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ "
"vādena vādaṃ āsādetabbaṃ amaññimha."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: Adhivāsetu → adhivāsetu ca (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "mn35:27.7"
msgid ""
"Adhivāsetu me bhavaṃ gotamo svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṃghenā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:27.8"
msgid "Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="nya" id="nya28"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli1.237"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc27"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:28.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā te licchavī "
"āmantesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:28.2"
msgid ""
"“suṇantu me bhonto licchavī, samaṇo me gotamo nimantito svātanāya saddhiṃ "
"bhikkhusaṅghena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:28.3"
msgid "Tena me abhihareyyātha yamassa patirūpaṃ maññeyyāthā”ti."
msgstr ""

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/on-dishes-of-meals-kings-and-offerings/3970
#. <a class="nya" id="nya29"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:29.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te licchavī tassā rattiyā accayena saccakassa nigaṇṭhaputtassa "
"pañcamattāni thālipākasatāni bhattābhihāraṃ abhihariṃsu."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:29.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho nigaṇṭhaputto sake ārāme paṇītaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ "
"paṭiyādāpetvā bhagavato kālaṃ ārocāpesi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:29.3"
msgid "“kālo, bho gotama, niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan”ti."
msgstr ""

#. <a class="nya" id="nya30"></a>
msgctxt "mn35:30.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya yena saccakassa "
"nigaṇṭhaputtassa ārāmo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi "
"saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:30.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṇītena "
"khādanīyena bhojanīyena sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:30.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavantaṃ bhuttāviṃ onītapattapāṇiṃ "
"aññataraṃ nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:30.4"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho saccako nigaṇṭhaputto bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/sharing-merit-a-note-on-punna-and-punnamahi/3972
msgctxt "mn35:30.5"
msgid ""
"“yamidaṃ, bho gotama, dāne puññañca puññamahī ca taṃ dāyakānaṃ sukhāya "
"hotū”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:30.6"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ kho, aggivessana, tādisaṃ dakkhiṇeyyaṃ āgamma avītarāgaṃ avītadosaṃ "
"avītamohaṃ, taṃ dāyakānaṃ bhavissati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mn35:30.7"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho, aggivessana, mādisaṃ dakkhiṇeyyaṃ āgamma vītarāgaṃ vītadosaṃ "
"vītamohaṃ, taṃ tuyhaṃ bhavissatī”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn35:30.8"
msgid "Cūḷasaccakasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ."
msgstr ""
